 love for travel and entertaining at home made starting VIETRI a natural!&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" class="gf_row gf_equal-height gf_row-gap-0" id="r-1638298011139" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1638298011139" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="0px" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1620143428165" data-id="1620143428165" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1638298011093" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1638298011093"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#ffffff">I first met Alessandro Taddei fifteen years ago and we became instant friends. We collaborated to create our classic holiday dinnerware pattern, Old St. Nick, who has become a beloved figure to both Alessandro and our VIETRI family as well as many tables and homes around the world. And so began our wonderful heirloom collection and the essence of our Old St. Nick Children's Book series.</font></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1620143428179" data-id="1620143428179" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1638298019091" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1638298019091" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/277745e7-0360-46b2-8518-6350083b4887/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/IMG_3319.jpeg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="